# placeholder — compiled WASM demo packages live here.
# Each demo is built to its own subdirectory, e.g.:
#
#   shell/static/demos/pong-76/
#     pong_76.wasm        ← compiled WASM binary
#     pong_76.js          ← wasm-bindgen JS glue
#     pong_76_bg.wasm     ← (if split into bg module)
#
# Build a demo by running from the project root:
#   .\build-demo.ps1 pong-76
#
# The shell loads these at runtime via dynamic import in ludeme-shell.ts.
# Never commit compiled WASM — it's generated output.
